title.narrative: Financial Sector Modernization and Information Management System

description.narrative: The objective of the Project is to assist the State Bank of Vietnam, the Credit Information Center and the Deposit Insurance of Vietnam to improve the delivery of their main functions in accordance with relevant international standards for the banking sector, through (a) developing a centralized and integrated system of advanced business processes and a modern information technology architecture; and (b) strengthening their institutional capacity in carrying out their operations.
